entry.title: Bitcoin-Qt/bitcoind version 0.8.3 released
entry.summary: On June 25th, 2013, Gavin Andresen announced the availability of Bitcoin-Qt version 0.8.3 on SourceForge, which can be downloaded from the provided link. The "splash" banner displays "0.8.3-BETA". The message is signed with a PGP signature, verifying its authenticity.
